<h2>GATE 0 — MANDATORY BEFORE EVERYTHING</h2>
<pre><code># Date — run this, use this, never memory:
(Get-Date).ToString('MMddyy')

# Week — compute from anchor:
$anchor=[DateTime]"2026-03-22"
$days=((Get-Date)-$anchor).Days
$index=[math]::Floor($days/7)%8
$names=@("A","E","B","F#","F","C","G","D")
Write-Host "Week: $($names[$index])"</code></pre>
<p>Calendar order: A → E → B → F# → F → C → G → D → repeat. Anchor: A Week = March 22, 2026.</p>
